## HerVoyage Co. environment variables (Vite)
## Copy this file to `.env` and paste your keys.

# CountryStateCity API key (free tier available)
# Get it from: https://app.countrystatecity.in/
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - Use CSC_API_KEY (NOT VITE_...) so it stays server-side (Vite proxy injects it).
# - Restart `npm run dev` after editing `.env`.
CSC_API_KEY="paste_your_key_here"

